data.description: Explore this well maintained split-level 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem! The main level features an open layout, ideal for hosting gatherings. The primary bedroom and bath are generously sized, offering a separate shower and a relaxing tub. Nestled in a quiet, non-HOA neighborhood, this home is conveniently close to shopping, schools, and I-20. Schedule a showing today!
